Name:          swift-IProto
Version:       %{__version}
Release:       %{!?__release:1}%{?__release}%{?dist}
Summary:       Swift implementation of iproto framed transport protocol

Group:         Development/Libraries
License:       MIT
URL:           https://github.com/my-mail-ru/%{name}
